==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: roadkill
<hw>road"kill</hw>, <pos>n. sing. & pl.</pos> <def>The body of an animal
killed by a vehicle on a road; <as>as, it is illegal in most places for
a restaurant to serve <ex>roadkill</ex> as food for people</as>. Also
used metaphorically; <as>as, ⟦ldquo⟧<ex>roadkill</ex> on the information
superhighway⟦rdquo⟧ (a person or corporation defeated by others more
expert at using the internet)</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Roadless</ent>⟦br⟧
